    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300004348_3_916-1016",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "916-1016",
      "markText": "文章是状态的流露，年轻的时候当然就流露出年轻的状态。状态一过，就再也写不到了。所以现在来改那时的文章，难下笔，越描越枯，不如不改。状态原来是不可以欺负的，它任性之极，就是丑，也丑得有志气，不得不敬它。",
      "totalCount": 1422,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300004348&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=916&rangeEnd=1016",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f8432ad0813ab6832g018e73?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=916&rangeEnd=1016"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300004348_17_2438-2512",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "2438-2512",
      "markText": "晓霞后来被打致死，罪名是勾引腐蚀红卫兵，背完全打烂，被初秋的苍蝇爬满。晓霞光着的两条腿上是第一次的血，苍蝇飞起来的时候，没有血的地方是安直梦里的白。",
      "totalCount": 1068,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300004348&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=2438&rangeEnd=2512",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f8432ad0813ab6832g018e73?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=2438&rangeEnd=2512"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300004348_3_2968-3037",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2968-3037",
      "markText": "青春难写，还在于写者要成熟到能感觉感觉。理会到感觉，写出来的不是感觉，而是理会。感觉到感觉，写出来才会是感觉。这个意思不玄，只是难理会得。",
      "totalCount": 930,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300004348&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2968&rangeEnd=3037",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f8432ad0813ab6832g018e73?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2968&rangeEnd=3037"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300004348_65_2324-2359",
      "chapterUid": 65,
      "range": "2324-2359",
      "markText": "我不管了，伸手就把锅盖揭了。水气散了，我看见了，锅里煮着个小孩儿的手。",
      "totalCount": 784,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300004348&chapterUid=65&rangeStart=2324&rangeEnd=2359",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f8432ad0813ab6832g018e73?chapterUid=65&rangeStart=2324&rangeEnd=2359"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300004348_3_2006-2041",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2006-2041",
      "markText": "我在这里写到昔日的青春同路人，想想当时都才十多岁，额头都是透明放光的。",
      "totalCount": 770,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300004348&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2006&rangeEnd=2041",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f8432ad0813ab6832g018e73?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2006&rangeEnd=2041"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300004348_3_2565-2604",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2565-2604",
      "markText": "忘了的东西一定是记不住的东西，这是废话，不过废话若由经验得来，就有废话的用处。",
      "totalCount": 752,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300004348&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2565&rangeEnd=2604",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f8432ad0813ab6832g018e73?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2565&rangeEnd=2604"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300004348_10_1842-1901",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "1842-1901",
      "markText": "琴没有装起来，因为螺钉不知道掉到哪里去了。拉弦钢板靠在队部的墙上，村里的小孩子用小石头扔，若打中了，嗡的一声，响好久。",
      "totalCount": 720,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300004348&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1842&rangeEnd=1901",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f8432ad0813ab6832g018e73?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1842&rangeEnd=1901"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300004348_3_816-887",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "816-887",
      "markText": "年轻气盛，年轻自然气盛，元气足。元气足，不免就狂。年轻的时候狂起来还算好看，二十五岁以后再狂，没人理了。孔子晚年有狂的时候，但他处的时代年轻。",
      "totalCount": 702,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300004348&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=816&rangeEnd=887",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f8432ad0813ab6832g018e73?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=816&rangeEnd=887"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300004348_3_2661-2734",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2661-2734",
      "markText": "不过依我的经验，青春这件事，多的是恶。这种恶，来源于青春是盲目的。盲目的恶，即本能的发散，好像老鼠的啃东西，好像猫发情时的搅扰，受扰者皆会有怒气。",
      "totalCount": 676,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300004348&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2661&rangeEnd=2734",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f8432ad0813ab6832g018e73?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2661&rangeEnd=2734"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300004348_5_554-581",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "554-581",
      "markText": "铃铛们又慌慌响起来，马帮如极稠的粥，慢慢流向那个山口。",
      "totalCount": 672,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300004348&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=554&rangeEnd=581",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f8432ad0813ab6832g018e73?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=554&rangeEnd=581"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300004348_6_3274-3305",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3274-3305",
      "markText": "阳光明晃晃地从云中垂下来，燃着了草岗上一块红的火，一块黄的火。",
      "totalCount": 612,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300004348&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3274&rangeEnd=3305",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f8432ad0813ab6832g018e73?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3274&rangeEnd=3305"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300004348_9_1784-1856",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "1784-1856",
      "markText": "因为天骂的菁华，无非是详细描述人体器官及其功能，上至祖先，下及孙儿，所谓诅咒，无非是器官的功能不得顺利发挥，或没有结果，或很困难，或，等等等等。",
      "totalCount": 608,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300004348&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1784&rangeEnd=1856",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f8432ad0813ab6832g018e73?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=1784&rangeEnd=1856"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300004348_12_2518-2548",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "2518-2548",
      "markText": "北大的正系鞋带儿，听问，说，我？专业对口，我读的是地球物理。",
      "totalCount": 602,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300004348&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=2518&rangeEnd=2548",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f8432ad0813ab6832g018e73?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=2518&rangeEnd=2548"
